preownedConditionTypes.conditionTypeDefinition: Item is in excellent condition, perfect working condition and has no signs of wear/usage. The original protective wrapping, if any, may be missing but the original packaging is intact.

Item is in excellent condition and has no signs of usage. The item is still in its original packaging, but packaging is open/has signs of wear. The item includes original accessories. This could include warehouse items, returns, etc.
Item shows wear from consistent use, but it remains in fair condition. The item may be marked, identified, or show other signs of previous use. The item remains usable.
A well-cared-for item that has seen limited use but remains in great condition. Item and instructions are complete and included.
A brand-new, unused functional item that has cosmetic imperfections caused during production or delivery. (Missing threads, discoloration, label malfunction, etc.)
A brand-new, unused item without original packaging.
A brand-new, unused item without original tags.
An original name brand cartridge that has been professionally cleaned, refilled with similar quality ink, and then tested to make sure you get the same print quality as the original cartridge.

_rawConfigs.preownedConditionSubHeadingContent: Walmart Pre-Owned allows you to find previously owned, well-cared-for items from Walmart’s trusted & performance-managed sellers. Shopping Pre-Owned allows you to bring home the best-quality picks at even lower prices, in addition to extending the life of an item & reducing waste. Find your favorites & shop a range of conditions in every category.

product.shortDescription: If you are planning to switch to an aluminum-free deodorant, then try Native Deodorant with over 15,000 5-Star Reviews. Native deodorant is aluminum-free and contains naturally derived ingredients, with effective long-lasting odor protection. We believe you should not have to choose between a deodorant that makes you feel safe and a deodorant that works. We never use aluminum, parabens, or sulfates in any of our products. At Native we use both safe, synthetic, sustainable fragrances (free of phthalates) and natural fragrances. Native: Clean. Simple. Effective.

customerReviews.reviewText: I have the mini size one of this and I am wearing it right now, lol. I was skeptical of something that was different and had aluminum. I don't know or understand the difference. What I do know is that this stuff goes on light, has a nice light scent to it, and it works beautifully! I have sensitive skin and a sensitive nose so finding something like this has made me really happy. I don't sweat when I'm wearing this and I feel fresh. Pretty happy with it.

I had doubts about trying this deodorant. I've had a very hard time finding a deodorant without aluminum that works for me. like worked for a short time for me but ended up not working long term. I am very pleased that this native deodorant works all day and into the next morning and smells very nice. It's a nice scent but not over powering.
It has only good ingredients and works just as well if not better than anti-perspirant at keeping stink away. All of their scents are great! My favorite is the cucumber and mint. Highly recommend.

I've tried 5 other brands of aluminum free, natural deodorants and this is the only brand that worked all day without causing an allergic reaction. I only found one other brand that worked all day and I had a huge reaction to it.
I would have been better off wearing nothing than wearing the rest I've tried. 
This deodorant smells great even after doing a workout in the southern summer heat. Now that's saying something!
Works great for me. I prefer Arm and Hammer. It is a nice change,  but over priced. Smells like yummy coconut vanilla.

We've been looking for a natural deodorant and found this product. My husband and I both love their products and they have several scents. Coconut vanilla is my husband's favorite.I bought a couple of time from native's website and I'm glad walmart carries it now

Part of this order did not arrive at our house as requested, but ended up as a curb side pickup at a Wal Mart 25 miles away. We did not specify to pick it up at the store. We wanted it shipped to our house. We were not able to pick it up, so that part of the order was cancelled. So we need to be reimbursed for the cancelled part of the order (The rest of the order, just the Ivory soap, arrived on time at our house). Oh, we cannot give a rating because we have not used the Ivory soap yet.

staining my clothes underams with an oily stain! be careful! my work sctubs are ruined!  I have tried 3 times to upload a picture but the Walmart website is glitching and it will not let me so sorry for no picture with my review.

Got this two months ago and dont recommend this for anybody of color. My under almost turned black dealing with this deodorant and my shirt under arms area smh horrible. And its heavy to put on feel like im spreading heavy thick peanut butter under there. Just to much!!!
